OL,4,Ccongratulates theatre on 25th
OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,FBroadcaster and author Melyvn Bragg
OL,8,Fhas congratulated a Cumbrian theatre
OL,9,Fon its 25th birthday and says the
OL,10,Ffacility is vital to the local area.
OL,12,FKeswick's Theatre by the Lake is
OL,13,Fcelebrating its anniversary by opening
OL,14,Fa picture exhibition, for one year,
OL,15,Ffeaturing 25 people who have worked
OL,16,Fwith the theatre. The exhibition
OL,17,Fincludes a picture of actress Dame
OL,18,FJudi Dench and Lord Melvyn Bragg.
OL,20,FDame Judi Dench officially opened the
OL,21,Ftheatre in Keswick, in 1999.
