OL,7,FProud Cumbrian Lord Melyvn Bragg is a
OL,8,Fpatron of the theatre and has been
OL,9,Fheavily involved in promoting arts.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've seen so many good
OL,12,Fproductions there, both in the main
OL,13,Ftheatre, in the studio.
OL,15,F"Local people have made it their own
OL,16,Fand make it work, and people come from
OL,17,Fall over. They get some of the best
OL,18,Fartists, directors and actors to come
OL,19,Fthere. It's been a triumph."
