OL,7,FDave Roberts, former manager at
OL,8,FTheatre by the Lake, spoke about how
OL,9,FDame Judi Dench became involved with
OL,10,Fthe Cumbrian theatre.
OL,12,FHe said: "Well Judi was involved
OL,13,Fbecause her husband Mike was a good
OL,14,Ffriend of Phil Kemp, who was on the
OL,15,Fboard.
