OL,7,F"So Phil got them involved on the
OL,8,Fpublicity side. So they came up on
OL,9,Fvarious occasions to do charity shows.
OL,10,FThen Judi said yes to being the
OL,11,Fpatron. That's always good on your
OL,12,Fletterhead really."
OL,14,FTheatre by the Lake first began with
OL,15,Fthe name 'Century Theatre', known as
OL,16,F'The Tick Box', in 1961.
OL,18,FLocal residents rallied around plans
OL,19,Fto build Theatre by the Lake, with the
OL,20,Fproject beginning in 1991, costing up
OL,21,Fto #6.5m.
