OL,7,FMartin Bellarby, who has volunteered
OL,8,Fat the theatre for 50 years, says the
OL,9,Fprevious building was "not fit for
OL,10,Fpurpose".
OL,12,FHe said: "The blue box was slowing
OL,13,Fdisintegrating, it couldn't survive.
OL,14,FIt was just not fit for purpose any
OL,15,Flonger really.
OL,17,F"So it was a very ambitious idea to
OL,18,Fraise enough money, there were quite a
OL,19,Fnumber of people involved and it took
OL,20,Fa few years in getting money together
OL,21,F- it cost a lot of money to do it."
