OL,7,FThe theatre stages a variety of
OL,8,Fdifferent productions, art classes and
OL,9,Fdifferent festivals.
OL,11,FActor Dave Hearn, who's playing
OL,12,FSherlock Holmes in Hound of the
OL,13,FBaskervilles at the theatre, believes
OL,14,Ftheatre is "a real hub of
OL,15,Fentertainment in Cumbria." He said: "I
OL,16,Fthink that's really important.
