OL,5,Canniversary
OL,7,F"But also to go through what we've all
OL,8,Fbeen through in the last couple years
OL,9,Fwith Covid and those sort of things,
OL,10,Fand to be able to recover and still
OL,11,Fdeliver shows is a testament to the
OL,12,Fstrength of the theatre and its
OL,13,Ftheatre."
OL,15,FThe new exhibition called 'We Are 25'
OL,16,Fdocuments the legacy and work of
OL,17,FCumbrian stories and experiences of
OL,18,Fpeople living in the region.
