OL,7,FLiz Stevenson, Artistic Director, says
OL,8,Fthe celebrations of their landmark
OL,9,Fbirthday will continue throughout the
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FShe said: "We've got lots of stuff
OL,13,Fplanned for our 25th anniversary year.
OL,14,FSo we've got 'Company 25', which is 14
OL,15,Fto 18 years old, 25 of them,
OL,16,Finterested in acting, design and
OL,17,Fwriting - saying what they want the
OL,18,Ffuture of Theatre by the Lake to be."
